RACE.FOOTNOTES: SUMMER CAT broke sharply then duel for the lead while two wide into the turn, was in a long sustained drive and proved best in a game effort. MY BABYS GONE chased the pace while three wide into the turn, angled inside in mid stretch but came up short in late stretch. MARIAH'S CANDY was inside into the turn, shied from the rail and pin balled around and taken up to be settled then made a mild rally in the stretch. ROZEY CHEEKS chased the early pace while inside into the turn then faltered. CHIKARA raced three wide on the turn and was no menace. A steward's inquiry was held concerning the run into the turn. After reviewing the film's, no action was taken.
